FEATURES
- scoring:
    - show how many players got the answer correct out of total players
    - show the player list with their avatars as a list
    - one second later show who got it correct and who got it wrong and showing their answers
    - one second later show the leaderboard update animation with their base scones
    - one second larer show the leaderboard update animation with their bonus scores

- host extra time control    
- player extra time request (later)
    - add an option to request for an extra 15 seconds on the player view
    - if everyone requests it, add 15 seconds to the timer. 
    - show a small counter of how many people have requested extra time on the host view.
- game pause
    - add a text on player view like "host is upto something..."
    - grey out the back during game pause on the player view
- sound effects
    - ticking sound during last 5 seconds
    - sound when time is up
    - sound when answer is submitted

## Code improvements
- Add types all across the app
- Custom components for buttons, modals, etc. to avoid code duplication
- Shared state in a global store (like Redux or Zustand) to avoid prop drilling
- Userprofile has name and so does gamePlayerSlice. Merge them into one.